attributes.title: [Ripsaw][SeqWrite] Fio execution
attributes.description:
This dashboard shows a fio execution with the following parameters:
    -Sequential: Write, Read and ReadWrite tests
    -Random: Write, Read and ReadWrite tests
    -Three samples

To get only one execution from our Elasticsearch index, we need to filter with the cluster_name field
